lead_paragraph: BOSTON -- With help from national fund-raising groups, Elizabeth Warren has already raised $3.15 million for her United States Senate campaign, catapulting ahead of her Democratic primary opponents.

headline.main: In Senate Race, Warren Raises More Cash Than Brown
